	"notes": "<p><br></p>",
	"history": "<p>Diogenis was fascinated early as a child by mechs and his father had worked using a civilian mech. He even got to see a demonstration put on by some newer, more maneuverable mechs at a show. Unfortunately his father passed away due to illness while he was still young and was taken into care by his grandparents. He never got along with his grandfather and left at the first chance he got. Got a job working on some mining colony moon. One of the only things he has left of his father was his old lunchpail which he brought with him. Working in the mines for years, he returned after hearing his grandmother had passed. After reconciliation between him and his grandfather, he decided to pursue a future working with mechs and hopefully pilot one day.</p>",
